e-full wp-image-142\" src=\"http://www.jinhuichengda.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/图片-23.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"774\" height=\"654\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>不是所有的米都有有机认证</strong>\r\n\r\n来自黑龙江通河大米\r\n\r\n真正的从源头上把控了品质！\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-82\" src=\"http://www.jinhuichengda.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/图片-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"729\" height=\"415\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>“</strong>健康稻-鲜活米<strong>”</strong><strong>的胚芽米好在哪？</strong>\r\n\r\n除了来源产地上的优势\r\n\r\n相对于传统的加工工艺\r\n\r\n“健康稻-鲜活米”更是突破传统！\r\n\r\n我们在超市买到的大米通常是精白米\r\n\r\n而“健康稻-鲜活米”能买到的是<strong>胚芽米</strong>！\r\n\r\n一张图看出区别！\r\n\r\n向上滑动查看胚芽米、精白米对比\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-141\" src=\"http://www.jinhuichengda.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/图片-24.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"983\" height=\"1033\" />\r\n\r\n胚芽米富含人体所需的多种维生素\r\n\r\n<strong>维生素B、维生素E、钙、铁、硒...</strong>\r\n\r\n长期食用胚芽米不仅<strong>营养丰富</strong>\r\n\r\n还可<strong>预防多种疾病</strong>、<strong>摆脱亚健康</strong>！\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-140\" src=\"http://www.jinhuichengda.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/图片-25.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"825\" height=\"263\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>选择“</strong>健康稻-鲜活米<strong>”</strong><strong>的6大理由</strong>\r\n\r\n这个项目很好，担心自己不会运营怎么办？\r\n\r\n“健康稻-鲜活米”总部支持，成就非凡致富之路！\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-139\" src=\"http://www.jinhuichengda.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/图片-26.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"746\" height=\"634\" />', '加盟知识', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '138-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-10-31 23:35:08', '2018-10-31 15:35:08', '', 138, 'http://www.jinhuichengda.com/?p=147', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
